KNetSwitch 0.1
==============

0.1) Purpose of this Program
0.2) Prerequisites


0.1 Purpose of this Program
===========================
See http://knetswitch.berlios.de

0.2 Prerequisites
=================
The following utilities must be present in /sbin:
 - ifconfig
 - route

Any distribution complying to the Filesystem Hierarchy Standard (FHS)
version 2.2 should have these utilities in the above location.

You will also need KDE 2.2.x (other 2.x versions should work as well).
KDE is available from http://www.kde.org

0.3 Installation
===============
./configure
make
make install (as root)


